            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "and if becoming the number one ranked assassin in the world wasn't enough, now it's time for Travis to become number one in the Galactic Superhero Rankings. When an intergalactic threat crashes down to Earth, it falls to our otaku anti-hero to save the world by putting an end to the evil Prince FU's lifelong dream of conquering the planet. Travis, welcome back to the Garden of Insanity!  ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
